            <p>For the following data, draw a scatter plot. If we wanted to know when the temperature would reach 28 °F, would the answer involve interpolation or extrapolation? Eyeball the line and estimate the answer.</p>
            <table xml:id="PRECALC-I7oDnISQ74" original="PRECALC/modules/m49327/index.cnxml" license="CC-BY-4.0">
