              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>2008</cell>
                <cell>8487</cell>
              </row>
              <row>
                <cell>2009</cell>
                <cell>9462</cell>
              </row>
            </tabular>
          </table>
        </statement>
        <solution>
          <p>Yes, trend appears linear because <m>r=0.\text{ 985 }</m> and will exceed 12,000 near midyear, 2016, 24.6 years since 1992.</p>
        </solution>
      </exercise>
  
